OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start for most with
OL,6,Fthe odd shower. Brightening up for
OL,7,Fsome by the afternoon but heavy slow-
OL,8,Fmoving showers may develop in Cornwall
OL,9,Fand west Devon. Feeling somewhat
OL,10,Fcooler in the light breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers in Cornwall and Devon
OL,13,Fwill ease, leaving a mostly dry night
OL,14,Fwith clear spells for many. Staying
OL,15,Frelatively mild. Showers returning to
OL,16,FCornwall by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
