OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FSome showers across Cornwall
OL,6,Ffirst thing which can be heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes. Otherwise a mostly dry day with
OL,8,Fbright spells. Isolated showers across
OL,9,FSomerset and Gloucestershire later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FScattered
OL,12,Fshowers on Friday, mainly in the
OL,13,Fafternoons, but staying dry for some.
OL,14,FLonger periods of rain are possible on
OL,15,FSaturday and Sunday. Turning warmer
OL,16,Fafter chilly nights at first.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
